edBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:51:30.000Z","msg":"點解Tvb可以癲倒是非？？？？？？？？？"},{"pid":"d053e738eeaa2abf68c24333ae81dd2e03071918","tid":1349950,"uid":265192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2x7DQUV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2x7DQUV.png&h=791635de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家好清楚我地武力升級有限，啲狗仲有好多武器未出，包括實彈同水炮車，呢啲傷害力好高，足以打散我地陣勢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">硬撼對我地係絕對不利</span><br />\n<br />\n遍地開花是有用的，最緊要係打<span style=\"color: red;\">消耗戰</span><br />\n<br />\n警察只有3萬個，佢地冇可能短時間補充到（除非佢地搵國安扮警察，但係數量唔會多，因為好難落命令同埋組織戰術）<br />\n<br />\n而家夏天佢地下下都出曬防暴裝，朝早企到夜，對佢地身心都造成好大負荷，相反我地可以休息，可以補給，人數多到可以輪住做<br />\n<br />\n我地一定要拎住個<span style=\"color: red;\">主導權</span><br />\n<br />\n1. Be water，唔好戀戰<br />\n<br />\n呢個講咗好耐，但而家唔係講緊執生咁簡單，而係要變成主動一方，撚狗式遊走。<br />\n<br />\n我地逼佢地動員，但唔好引佢地升級武力。喺清場之前我地可以好似以前咁挑釁。<span style=\"color: red;\">當我地逼到佢地要清場嘅時候，我地就要毫不猶豫即刻散</span>，唔好戀戰。<span style=\"color: red;\">可以轉換場地，等佢地重新佈防，又或者留力去第二日</span><br />\n<br />\n總之我地<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好畀時間佢地休息</span>，雖然我地都會有體力消耗，但同佢地比我地會消耗得慢好多<br />\n<br />\n如果啲狗好似七一咁突然走曬去休息呢？我地就唔好畀機會佢地休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即刻升級，逼曬佢地翻出嚟之後又走，令佢地keep住精神繃緊<br />\n<br />\n2. 單一焦點，唔好浪費彈藥<br />\n<br />\n每一次行動都應該事先傾好，制定一個明確嘅目標。<span style=\"color: red;\">當是日目標達成之後，唔好即日觸發第二個事件</span>！好似琴日咁，噴黑國徽同臨時立法會宣言相衝，喺港島嘅焦點就去曬國徽度，我地又浪費咗一粒彈藥。"},{"pid":"985f9a7b7bf54b9ee4cbb42445e0ac0d125b9a6b","tid":1349950,"uid":273923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b3beacb6ef5ab5c7251adbcf5f907368b63d8809","tid":1349950,"uid":75067,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:35:24.000Z","msg":"完全冇人提tvb"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:54:22.000Z","msg":"因為完全無睇TVB"},{"pid":"4f00ed2f51450937f052ecafbc59c571133f963b","tid":1349950,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:54:42.000Z","msg":"btw 36槍呢個now係咪都冇報<br />\n定我睇漏"},{"pid":"52ffd4f33d9fde35800768eefd317070673c1b86","tid":1349950,"uid":239250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:55:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe1adb262a76317438249aba02b68606c1792519","tid":1349950,"uid":278463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:55:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">CCTVB 昨晚新聞仲話係有兩批人在元朗站毆鬥！ 什麼兩批人毆鬥？ 根本就是無辜市民被黑社會毆打，而黑警就縱容及袖手旁觀！😡</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2db1c0fc325cbe64057d7362c49673d7f1c3df8a","tid":1349950,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ba1f55d2c2d890084e80e2c9bfb97d2801c997","tid":1349950,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:02:06.000Z","msg":"辭職啦DLLM"},{"pid":"1a2e702abdaaa55bef66838a0ffb63b41ba768d0","tid":1349950,"uid":213059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:03:50.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"14c8c198ef8f95d71985522a23c85e22c9232519","tid":1349950,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1249d2da043694f1c2c683c54d36aab9b51091f6","tid":1349950,"uid":1748,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:04:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7727b0f2ee720eca0b84446dd25394